parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.What? I’m just saying… could use a cleaning.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.Ugh. Wait here. I’ll change and get the files.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.What a mess… She could use a maid.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp<.The computer is on. She’s been working on Saturday?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlOp<.Do I dare try and guess her password?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.This is what we have. Let’s get to work.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I found an ID on the floor in the kitchen.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.I’ve been around the place a few times.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Expired last year. Not sure how it got into the Wilkes’ kitchen unless it belongs to one of those creepy lepers.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Your computer is plugged into the station’s network?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaOp.A privilege I’m sure you’ll get once Andrea promotes you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlOp.You think I have a promotion coming?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnOp.I have no idea what you and her have planned.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.Eclipse Guild… A warrant was issued last year but… no one was found.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.Well… It’s clear to me what’s going on.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Those lepers are former Guild… All of them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Charles was a Guild leader and those were his men…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Madalyn came in and took over. Brainwashing the whole crew.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.Kimura isn’t going to want to hear that.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.Come on. Let’s go over what we have.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.Would it kill you to smile every now and then?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnDe.I have never in my life been driven so insane by one person.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.I’ll dry your damned clothes. Let’s get moving so we don’t keep Andrea waiting.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McHaOp.Holy hell! That woman is a good fuck.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.I better read up. I can’t let Andrea down.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.So, as far as we know, Charles died of a heart attack.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.And don’t forget that Charles had a search warrant served at his home…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaOp.There’s a lot of evidence here. I suspect he was involved with the Guild. But a leader?...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaOp.No. If we aren’t positive, we aren’t telling Kimura.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.I’ll meet you at Andrea’s at seven.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Lillian! She was here! She… took my cum!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeWoCl.How the hell did she get in here?... Where the hell did she go?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.You said this place was haunted. You’re not as wrong as I thought.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.She’s with Kimberly, in the Channel 4 building.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.We have to make sure she’s okay!...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnOpNo1.What the hell were you thinking? We were so close to finding a way into the Guild bunker.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.It’s over, Melissa. Andrea will take it from here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnDe.Like hell, she is. I don’t trust her. Why isn’t she telling me what’s going on?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaDe.Fuck… You’re right… Andrea is not following the law.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I’m part of her undercover team now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.Well, what the hell am I supposed to do? This is my only option to stay on the case.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaOp.What are her orders? What’s she hiding?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnOp.We’re past that now. I’m going behind her back with or without you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.She wants me to kill everyone… The whole North Santiva Eclipse Guild.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaEx.And make it look like a bust gone bad.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.The Guild has been here for years. She doesn’t want that on her record.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaOp.What am I going to do? I don’t want to do it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.We don’t need Andrea to make a bust. I can do it without her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.You’re going to make a move on the warehouse first? Before Andrea’s orders?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.It wouldn't be easy. But we have to know what we're getting into.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.Perhaps… Unless Miss Foxx were to credit the both of us with the bust.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlOp.I like the way you think. Let’s become the heroes before Andrea has any chance to paint the narrative.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.Andrea is only protecting herself. If she loses her job as commissioner, it’s her own fault.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.So what are we going to do?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.I need access to the Guild files.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.David and I lost access last week.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.Andrea doesn’t memorize her passwords. She keeps everything on a thumb drive.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.You want me to steal her thumb drive?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlDe.You’re goddamned right I can handle it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.I don’t know. But you’re closer to her than I am. You’re our best bet.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.The clock is ticking. I could be called to raid the bunker at any moment.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.Get me that thumb drive and I’m sure I can find something that will give us the warrant we need to start the raid early.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.I hope this works. There are lives depending on it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.Steal the thumb drive from Andrea so we can break into the Guild files.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.I won’t get in your way if you feel the need to help that thief. But don’t expect me to like it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.We’ll both need a little luck, I think.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaOp.Well? Did you get the thumb drive?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.She left it in her safe. I can’t believe I was able to break in…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlDe.Aren’t you interested in how I got it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiWoEx^.I tailed you here, 1Hero… I need help.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Enemies of the Guild and the ones who plan to assassinate Duncan.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I saw Henry in the bunker… He saved my life unintentionally.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiSaOp^.I know this might send us to jail, but I’m out of options.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlDe.I’m not on the force anymore. So unless Melissa arrests you…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.Do you know where the entrance is to the bunker?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.If we take her to a judge, she can help us justify a warrant…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.We can raid the warehouse, arrest the Guild and then this would all be over.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiSaDe^.It would be the last thing Henry and I do before going to prison.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.If you want to save him, then end the Guild here and now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.Is there any other way? I’d wager that Jon has every angle covered. He’s going to be clean.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.When you get the call from Andrea to move in, the whole Guild will be waiting in the warehouse.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.Yeah, and Nellie and I will be there.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.Whatever Andrea has planned, get Nellie to stall…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.I’ll send a unit there to investigate an anonymous tip.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Nellie’s not going to risk getting sent back to prison. She’s willing to do what it takes…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.Andrea needs to be held accountable for fucking up this case.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnDe.I won’t stand by and let her play executioner to save face.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiSaEx^.You said he saved your life… Get him out of there, 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaEx^.Meet me where you met the girl in black. I can help.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.I… I don’t know what she means.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I’ll talk to Nellie… She won’t like it, but maybe I can talk her into stalling.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.Don’t get into trouble, 1Hero. You’ve been a pain in the ass, but you’ve been a good man, I must admit.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.Give me the word, and I’ll have officers swarm the warehouse.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.I will. It’s the right thing to do.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.There are some small issues in the kitchen.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnOp.Give me more time… Stop bothering me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McHaEx.All done! Your shitty condo is slightly less shitty now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Damn! That went from zero to a hundred real quick.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.What can we do, 1Hero? The odds are stacked against us. No one’s going to believe what’s happening until it’s too late.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.We’ll stop Lilith and destroy the Toma Leolo.");
